data.description:
Solid money making two family property, perfect for investors or owner occupied! Each unit has month to month tenants and boasts 2 bedrooms, large living rooms, dining rooms with eat in kitchen. Full walk up attic that could be finished as well as a dry basement great for storage/laundry.
Plenty of off street parking in the driveway with vacant corner lot included in the sale!
Pre qualification/ POF and 24 hour notice required for all showings.
